@node History "History"

@{b}History@{ub}

@{b}v0.2 (03.07.96)@{ub}
 * Initial release.

@{b}v0.3 (07.07.96)@{ub}
 * Command arguments corrected.
 * Break with CTRL-C disabled.
 * Font for textfield.gadget selectable.

@{b}v0.4 (09.07.96)@{ub}
 * "Include" didn't set modified flag.
 * Calvin improved. :)
 * A public screen is selectable.
 * Window not opened until all options are set.

@{b}v0.5 (10.07.96)@{ub}
 * Save made working again.
 * Fixed bug making only the editor window open on the selected screen.

@{b}v1.0 (15.08.96)@{ub} Bumped revision to @{i}finished@{ui} version.
 * A base for MUI selectable.
 * Added an option to clear contents of the editor.
 * Added ARexx support.

@endnode


